                    <h3>The Wall Street Journal</h3>
                    <p>Article - 'Japan is Changing How We'll Grow old (360 Video)'</p>
                    <p><small>Interaction Design Style:</small></p>
                    <p>User is stationary with control of the camera with head movement</p>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-5 offset-md-1 order-1 order-md-2">
                    <img class="img-fluid" src="/src/images/research1/TheWallStreet.jpg" alt="">
                </div>
            </div>

            
            <div class="row py-5 align-items-center">
                <div class="col-md-5 offset-md-1 order-2 order-md-1 mt-4 mt-lg-0">
