                </div>

                <div class="col-md-5 offset-md-1  order-md-1 order-2  mt-4 mt-lg-0">
                    <h3>Land’s End Game</h3>
                    <p><small>Interaction Design Style:</small></p>
                    <p>User’s movements are controlled by fixating on key objects or in game prompts.</p>
                </div>

