        <div class="container py-5 text-center text-md-left" data-aos="zoom-in-down">
          <h2 class="display-2 mb-1 projects__header text-center pb-lg-5 pb-md-3">Simulator Sickness Questionnaire</h2>
          <div class="row py-5 align-items-center">
              <div class="col-md-5 offset-md-1 order-md-1 order-2 mt-4 mt-lg-0">
                  <h3>Simulator Sickness Questionnaire</h3>
                  <p><small>Why test this?</small></p>
                  <p>Exposure to virtual reality can cause symptoms similar to motion sickness. I wanted to see if there was a relationship between interaction type and symptoms of simulation sickness.</p>
              </div>
              <div class="col-md-5 offset-md-1 order-1 order-md-2">
